==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: chandelle
<hw>chandelle</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Aeronautics)</fld> <def>an abrupt
climbing turn made by an airplane, in which the plane's momentum is used
to achieve a higher than normal rate of climb, without stalling the
aircraft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>chandelle</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: chandelle
<hw>chandelle</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>to perform a chandelle, as of
an airplane.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

